HEADWORD: Nomology
<hw>No*mol"o*gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>no`mos</grk> law + <ets>-logy</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The science of law; legislation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The science of the laws of the mind; rational
psychology.</def> <rj><au>Sir W. Hamilton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nomopelmous</ent>⟦br⟧
